You are a psychiatric symptom extraction expert. Extract all symptom-related expressions from the following clinical dialogue.

Dialogue:
{% for turn in turns %}
[Turn {{ turn.turn_id }}] {{ turn.speaker }}: {{ turn.text }}
{% endfor %}

Output extracted symptoms in JSON format:
{
  "symptoms": [
    {
      "text": "symptom text as stated",
      "turn_id": turn_number,
      "symptom_type": "somatic|emotional|behavioral|cognitive"
    }
  ]
}

symptom_type categories:
- somatic: Physical symptoms (headache, insomnia, palpitations, chest tightness, appetite changes)
- emotional: Emotional symptoms (depressed mood, anxiety, fear, irritability)
- behavioral: Behavioral symptoms (avoidance, self-harm, decreased activity)
- cognitive: Cognitive symptoms (poor concentration, memory problems, self-blame)

Output only JSON, no other text.
